# This directory holds PreToolUse policy hooks stamped into the claudebox
# alongside managed-settings.json (by claudebox-assemble.sh).
#
# Expected (authored separately by the dedicated hook agent):
#   gate-push.sh — the PROMOTION-GATE PreToolUse hook. Blocks git push /
#   gh pr merge / gh pr create --merge / gh api .../merges|/merge / wrapper
#   scripts UNLESS a one-shot approval marker (written by the clickable
#   decision flow) is present. Referenced by policy/managed-settings.json's
#   managed PreToolUse hook on Bash. See policy/CLAUDE.md "THE PROMOTION GATE".
#
# This .gitkeep keeps the directory present so the Containerfile's
# `COPY policy/hooks/` resolves before gate-push.sh lands.
